Welcome to Central Bedfordshire Liberal Democrats
Central Bedfordshire Liberal Democrats work hard all year round for communities across Central Bedfordshire.
In the 2023 local elections, the Lib Dems won 10 council seats on Central Bedfordshire Council - gaining 7 seats from the Conservatives.
We campaign to make our area a better place to live. You can find out more about our work and also contact us using this website.
You can also sign up for email updates at the bottom of the page.
